{{>common-topbar "contribute"}}

<div class="row" role="main" id="main" tabindex="0">
  <div class="column medium-12">
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Contribute to the Unified Listing</h3>
      <p>Contributions to the Unified Listing are welcome.  Follow the steps below to contribute new products or changes to existing product records.</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Register and Log In</h3>
    <p>
       To contribute information about products, you must <a href="/signup">create an account</a> and <a href="/login">log in</a>.
       During the signup process, you must provide an email address.  We will not share this address, it will only be used to contact you if there are questions about the information you submit.
    </p>

    <h3>Search for Existing Products</h3>
    <p>
       The Unified Listing contains information about thousands of existing products.  To find out if a product is listed, please use the <a href="/search">product search.</a>
    </p>
    <p>If you find your product and would like to contribute changes to the information we have available, use the "contribute change" link displayed next to the product.</p>

    <h3>Add a New Product</h3>
    <p>
       If a product is not already in the Unified Listing, please take the time to <a href="/contribute">contribute a new product</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

